00:57:01.720 --> 00:57:02.640
and in their mind

00:57:02.640 --> 00:57:05.720
that we would call them bad or evil.

00:57:06.280 --> 00:57:07.480
And then there's a second

00:57:07.480 --> 00:57:09.000
layer to question.

00:57:09.000 --> 00:57:12.000
Is there cosmic principle of evil?

00:57:12.640 --> 00:57:13.560
Now, I don't personally

00:57:13.560 --> 00:57:14.400
I don't believe there's

00:57:14.400 --> 00:57:16.680
