00:57:36.720 --> 00:57:38.880
I don't think of that as evil

00:57:40.080 --> 00:57:40.720
sunlight.

00:57:40.720 --> 00:57:43.640
And okay, if you want to call it evil,

00:57:43.640 --> 00:57:45.800
I would just call it

00:57:45.800 --> 00:57:48.800
the regressive side of the tension

00:57:49.200 --> 00:57:52.200
of our developmental capacity.

00:57:52.440 --> 00:57:55.840
What happens to individuals who have done

00:57:55.840 --> 00:57:59.040
so much damage to other individuals who,

00:57:59.880 --> 00:58:02.880
in exalting themselves health

00:58:03.080 --> 00:58:05.320
have hurt the lives of thousands

00:58:05.320 --> 00:58:07.680
and millions of people?

00:58:07.680 --> 00:58:10.760
Well, here I would turn to Michael Newton

00:58:11.520 --> 00:58:13.040
and Michael Newton in his book

00:58:13.040 --> 00:58:14.200
Destiny of souls.

00:58:14.200 --> 00:58:16.760
His first book was journey of the soul

00:58:16.760 --> 00:58:18.000
or Journey of Souls second

00:58:18.000 --> 00:58:19.680
book, Destiny of souls.

00:58:19.680 --> 00:58:21.960
He describes in more detail

00:58:21.960 --> 00:58:24.280
what happens to individuals

00:58:24.280 --> 00:58:25.800
who have been,

00:58:25.800 --> 00:58:28.800
who have given themselves over to malice

00:58:28.800 --> 00:58:31.440
injury, those type of things.

00:58:31.440 --> 00:58:34.440
And he says they require special handling

00:58:34.560 --> 00:58:37.040
because they're they are so distant.

00:58:37.040 --> 00:58:38.200
They have pulled away

00:58:38.200 --> 00:58:41.080
so far from their divine center,

00:58:41.080 --> 00:58:42.520
because when we are

00:58:42.520 --> 00:58:44.080
near the divine Center,

00:58:45.760 --> 00:58:46.880
it's a place of deep

00:58:46.880 --> 00:58:48.720
and profound compassion.

00:58:48.720 --> 00:58:50.280
It's the divine center

00:58:50.280 --> 00:58:52.480
is the touchstone of oneness.

00:58:52.480 --> 00:58:55.040
With oneness comes compassion

00:58:55.040 --> 00:58:57.120
comes at all inclusiveness.

00:58:57.120 --> 00:58:59.280
So someone who is

00:58:59.280 --> 00:59:02.280
pathological or malevolent in history

00:59:02.640 --> 00:59:05.640
is very far away from their divine center

00:59:05.680 --> 00:59:08.680
and therefore requires special handling

00:59:09.360 --> 00:59:10.920
when they die

00:59:10.920 --> 00:59:13.000
in order to handle the damage

00:59:13.000 --> 00:59:14.760
which they've done to themselves

00:59:14.760 --> 00:59:16.680
and to the people around them.

00:59:16.680 --> 00:59:19.240
Now, one simple way of understanding

00:59:19.240 --> 00:59:22.240
what happens to us when we die,

00:59:22.520 --> 00:59:23.280
and I draw this

00:59:23.280 --> 00:59:24.840
from looking at near-death

00:59:24.840 --> 00:59:26.320
episode literature.

00:59:26.320 --> 00:59:27.560
When people experience

00:59:27.560 --> 00:59:28.800
a life review,

00:59:28.800 --> 00:59:30.360
when people have the experience

00:59:30.360 --> 00:59:32.200
of their life review,

00:59:32.200 --> 00:59:34.600
they not only experience every second,

00:59:34.600 --> 00:59:35.640
every intention,

00:59:35.640 --> 00:59:38.000
every thought of their entire life,

00:59:38.000 --> 00:59:40.560
but they experience how those actions

00:59:40.560 --> 00:59:42.480
and how those thoughts impacted

00:59:42.480 --> 00:59:43.960
those around them.

00:59:43.960 --> 00:59:45.000
So someone who was in

00:59:45.000 --> 00:59:47.280
a fistfight experiences

00:59:47.280 --> 00:59:48.600
how the other person

00:59:48.600 --> 00:59:50.720
experienced being beaten up

00:59:50.720 --> 00:59:52.400
and what it did to their psyche,

00:59:52.400 --> 00:59:53.920
and where

00:59:53.920 --> 00:59:54.720
what happened

00:59:54.720 --> 00:59:57.000
when they brought that anger home.

00:59:57.000 --> 00:59:59.040
People who are in war,

00:59:59.040 --> 01:00:01.880
who have assassinated people, experience

01:00:01.880 --> 01:00:02.480
in their life.

01:00:02.480 --> 01:00:05.760
Review what that assassination did

01:00:05.760 --> 01:00:07.280
to the history of the family

01:00:07.280 --> 01:00:08.880
that was without a father.

01:00:08.880 --> 01:00:10.800
From that point on.

01:00:10.800 --> 01:00:12.800
So one way of thinking about this

01:00:12.800 --> 01:00:14.800
is if you just take a big rock

01:00:14.800 --> 01:00:16.760
and throw it into a lake

01:00:16.760 --> 01:00:18.680
and the ripples spread out,

01:00:18.680 --> 01:00:19.960
our life is like that.

01:00:19.960 --> 01:00:22.040
We send ripples out into the world.

01:00:23.280 --> 01:00:24.160
What happens when

01:00:24.160 --> 01:00:25.120
we die

01:00:25.120 --> 01:00:26.480
is that all those ripples

01:00:26.480 --> 01:00:28.040
come back to us,

01:00:28.040 --> 01:00:29.160
and we experience

01:00:29.160 --> 01:00:32.280
the full social impact of our lives.

01:00:32.880 --> 01:00:35.880
Not to punish us, not even to reward us,

01:00:36.120 --> 01:00:39.120
but because fundamentally, at core,

01:00:39.640 --> 01:00:41.840
life is one.

01:00:41.840 --> 01:00:43.800
And if you have lived your life

01:00:43.800 --> 01:00:45.520
according to that value

01:00:45.520 --> 01:00:47.440
and have tried to be good and careful

01:00:47.440 --> 01:00:48.120
