01:00:52.000 --> 01:00:55.000
It comes back to you and you experience

01:00:55.400 --> 01:00:56.120
the bliss,

01:00:56.120 --> 01:00:59.120
what we would call heaven or the bliss of

01:00:59.640 --> 01:01:02.560
of one's spiritual well-being.

01:01:02.560 --> 01:01:05.560
If you've done evil and harm and injury,

01:01:05.840 --> 01:01:08.840
